{"tid":378792,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［每晚1:40不明巨響］油塘撚入","createTime":"2017-08-28T17:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T20:53:43.000Z","uid":41602,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61b179ef72ffdfcc44f83f4c30d3177f29e6a112","tid":378792,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:48:39.000Z","msg":"大約係一個月前，我每晚呢個鐘數都未訓<br />\n<br />\n而係差唔多呢個時間點，我都會聽到外面一聲巨響<br />\n每晚都有<br />\n<br />\n而果種巨響係類似天邊行雷既聲音<br />\n<br />\n我真係想知究竟個下巨響係邊度發出黎同點解會係呢個時間點發出<br />\n<br />\n而我居住既地點係油麗邨對正東區隧道<br />\n<br />\n究竟係我每晚幻聽定真係有發生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無油塘撚幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6206af2343dcf54b917902fc5f04910e0ed98634","tid":378792,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"聽晚我嘗試下係窗口錄影<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc6eb2a81ff93f8e9abab7f40e12abc8c47cf0b","tid":378792,"uid":123274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:54:00.000Z","msg":"好似做緊將軍澳&ndash;藍田隧道爆石工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1efe6922642622061bd9c775612729c06c1460","tid":378792,"uid":22685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"我住秀麗但聽唔到喎"},{"pid":"0dcf73c4ee9637e5b40c0002cf62db967121d5c8","tid":378792,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似做緊將軍澳&ndash;藍田隧道爆石工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夜晚爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c195faa9badcb934996a854c2fa859cb6ee5e60","tid":378792,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:59:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似做緊將軍澳&ndash;藍田隧道爆石工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夜晚爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係似爆石果種聲<br />\n<br />\n但夜晚爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要正係爆一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f2cd29ba7bf495d4b8dd215ed522bc0a8e0a03","tid":378792,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我住秀麗但聽唔到喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽晚1:30左右留心聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e64fa4f87ed29906df4fdcd0bddac2ecce5cd4","tid":378792,"uid":57700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:00:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dab50783ee397e5d9706d2c580a661e6bfdbf282","tid":378792,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放左屁,唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你 洗唔洗每晚都咁準時放呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講多少少....早期聽我以為行雷.....然後果幾晚心諗...屌你又行雷咁！？咁多雷既！？</span>"},{"pid":"7e9f89e91a5b07b3f132d2d96db631a6866d8f65","tid":378792,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:06:42.000Z","msg":"我射得太大力震到你地板，唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 住你樓下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好找我悔氣ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5032f62516bd3b1d3395f41f14b677d34ed1b85b","tid":378792,"uid":41602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:08:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我朋友幫我搵到d咁既資料！第1.2.3！<br />\n<br />\n真係爆石聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/29/020724_54e70aae751afcc520f6e8423b16e089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F020724_54e70aae751afcc520f6e8423b16e089.jpg&h=6c84bcdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92c8d4f56b6ba7633c49b9da7332ea4bddf0a793","tid":378792,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:15:59.000Z","msg":"我再睇土木二程果邊既資料，話預計2019年中落成<br />\n<br />\n哇...屌你老母！仲要爆成年！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a80ef65c794f6a32a51cce304d98fdd9a56e55a","tid":378792,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:15:25.000Z","msg":"油塘撚準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n差唔多時間爆啦"},{"pid":"8556329bcf9b5e4cdc8c14f0d7e134a3e14be6a8","tid":378792,"uid":59462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:43:08.000Z","msg":"1:40 又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e802791f577b96c2beb5da40ea152cae5c3d71f","tid":378792,"uid":29612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:52:58.000Z","msg":"我想知東隧隔離座山起緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b767d07e40519ab32839c66700cb3fa8f8c3e1","tid":378792,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:56:40.000Z","msg":"有地盤行24，多數唔近民居"},{"pid":"c692ec45dff392d29e8dab605a56bee82ba69302","tid":378792,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi